window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Betrayed by blood. Bound by destiny.</p> <p>In a world where family secrets unravel and identities shatter, Troy’s life takes an unexpected turn. His home is no longer a sanctuary, and his family’s truths are nothing but a web of lies. Cast adrift with only a battered ship, a cryptic name, and a distant destination, Troy embarks on a perilous journey to unravel the mysteries of his past.</p> <p>Taking quests from unlikely allies, and with enemies lurking in every shadow, Troy must learn to pilot not just his ship but to rule his own fate. Confronting his future head-on—it’s clear there’s only one option—he will become the most powerful entity in the universe…or he will die in the attempt.</p>"; 
